Cisco-IOS-XR-evpn-oper API API Reference

API generated from Cisco-IOS-XR-evpn-oper@2018-09-26.yang

API Endpoint
http://{Controller-IP}:{Controller-Port}/restconf/operational/network-topology:network-topology/topology/topology-netconf/node/{{router}}/yang-ext:mount/
URL '/' code: %2F
Schemes: http
Version: 1.0.0

Paths

EVPN - Retrieve

GET Cisco-IOS-XR-evpn-oper:evpn/

Retrieve operation of resource: evpn

200 OK
evpn_schema

Successful operation

400 Bad Request

Internal Error

in path

node_schema

400 Bad Request
